Michel Platini suggests UEFA Euro 2020 could be spread across the continent. (BBC)France midfielder Samir Nasri criticises the media after his team's quarter-final exit to Spain, saying "you are always looking for shit, you write nothing but shit in your papers". His comments came after a L'Equipe journalist wrote an article that upset Nasri's mother. (AFP via NDTV) (BBC) (Al Jazeera)